    $aboutE7 = "Syn Studio wishes to thank the dozens of top concept artists and educators worldwide who met with us to advise us in the creation of an elite concept art training program. In particular we wish to give thanks to the legendary concept artist and world renowned educator <strong> Scott Robertson</strong> for generously donating his time and sharing his expertise with us on several occasions. We’d also like to thank the following artists and educators, mentioned in the “special thanks” sections of our application to the Ministry of Education, who officially participated in the process of developing and evaluating our program and application for accreditation.";
